 today's Syrian coast, referring to the geographical origin of the isolates)</s></p><p class="description"><s>Chemoorganotroph.</s><s>Acid produced from glucose.</s><s>Hydrolyzes arginine.</s><s>Does not hydrolyze urea.</s><s>Phosphatase positive.</s><s>Haemadsorbs guinea pig erythrocytes.</s><s>Film-and-spot positive.</s><s>Cholesterol required for growth.</s><s>Facultative anaerobe.</s><s>Temperature range, 20 to 37°C; temperature optimum, 28 to 32°C.</s><s>Isolated from periwinkles that were naturally infected in various locations along the Syrian coastal area.</s><s>The G+C content of the DNA is 26±1 mol%.</s><s>Type strain: strain P40<sup>T</sup> (=ATCC 43115<sup>T</sup>).</s></p></content></protolog>